Sample_treatment_protocol_ch1: Cells were infected with EBV with EBNA+ strain and EBNA2- strain, respectively.
Sample_growth_protocol_ch1: Cells were cultured in 10% FBS supplemented RPMI medium 1640 for 2 weeks.
Sample_extract_protocol_ch1: RNA was depleted of ribosomal RNA and sequenced at Cincinnati Children’s Hospital Medical Center (CCHMC) DNA Sequencing and Genotyping Core Facility. For ChIP-seq, libraries were prepared via ChIPmentation (Schmidl et al. 2015).  ATAC-seq libraries were prepared using the standard protocol (Buenrostro et al. 2015). HiChIP-seq libraries were prepared following Mumbach et al. (Mumbach et al. 2016).
Sample_data_processing: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: mango files (long-range interaction files) were generated using hichipper (version: 0.7.3) (http://aryeelab.org/hichipper)
Sample_contact_address: 3333 Burnet Ave, CCHMC, The CAGE, MLC 15012 c/o Ted, 200 BL
